      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited as a dedicated project car or for parts. The exterior suffers from significant rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with multiple large dents and heavily faded paint. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul, and the transmission exhibits slipping; additionally, the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. A buyer should expect to tow this vehicle and invest considerable time and resources to return it to a drivable state.",
